Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}老！師！目標瞄准！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:37.07,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}潛力越高 麻煩越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:42.56,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}dropout mentality 凌駕於非日常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:47.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們帶著一臉睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:52.42,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}背後藏著匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.92,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:57.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:03.38,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}多少帶著旁觀的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:11.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:22.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:27.34,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:32.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:38.57,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}殺意就是唯一給你的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:44.12,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}依靠（認真）自己（上吧）革命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.16,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}老！師！目標瞄准！
